Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是运动服部的铁则
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从驾驶舱里出来待机 以上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再从头说一遍
