Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连法洛斯一起攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的很明确呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还特地跑来宣战..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是残骸啊
