Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残骸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:56.43,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,660)}debri
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是宇宙的垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确切的说是长久以来与我们结为同盟的星球的原王族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在是名为奇斯的犯罪集团的头领
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单而言 就是敌人的幕后黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可谓人生无常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天亮之前也就是说..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据昨天的日没时刻来看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩5小时左右的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假设我们按照他的要求破坏了沃克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:23.35,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(940,660)}vox
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为敌人会乖乖地离开地球吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只会让我们失去唯一能与他们抗衡的手段而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路了 这里也太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田所先生 请好好听着我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆奇娜美啊 是我的..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡部小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请寻找一片适合战斗的安全海域
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非战斗人员的避难一结束我们就前往那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯向财团的全部支部通报情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严格管制战斗区域 不准任何船舶以及航空器进入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上原和京乃以及拉芬蒂一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快完成沃克斯的最终检查使其随时可以出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:13.00,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,660)}vox
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在发什么呆？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底抗战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆圈~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 兰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是马上就会出击..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报仇吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸发来的短讯上是这么写的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..没事..什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人摸不着头脑的是这个叫维拉裘里奥的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么特地跑出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 经你这么一说还真有些奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:35.82,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}鸭川能量饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我喝了就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙干什么..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝喝看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道蛮有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 我就..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我来..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这样的东西了解敌人也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基里乌斯？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始..口感不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至略感清爽..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是到达胃部的瞬间..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深不见底的甜味席卷而来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这个星球不可小看！伊泽！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个大惊小怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还蛮顺口的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 真的是去干什么去的..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离天亮还有差不多两小时吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么..到时就会揭晓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在几点？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能睡的时候不睡一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体会撑不住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量的话..我这多得是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说姆奇娜美？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 如果是那孩子的话 一点小事是不会气馁的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会啦 那是当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被说得那么过分论谁都会..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前他明明不可能会说那种话..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志向远大 又能体谅别人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前怎样都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我哪知道那个裘裘的过去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圆说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我有足够的理由和他战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打倒他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那..给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满格了再上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛..是前妻啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人也是嘴上不饶人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常常把我骂得狗血淋头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 直到现在心生寂寞时回忆起来还有些不寒而栗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 到了那种时候啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是NOVUMUNDUS日本分部的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找小圆的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要找的是她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到敌势的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请所有人员进入战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍 确认到敌势的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请所有人员进入战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方母舰的位置在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs48}他们一边保持着与本舰相同的相对速度一边在卫星轨道上移动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样为什么还不打过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得我说过非战斗人员要下船避难吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是那孩子的亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和两位机师连接通信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人基本就在我们的正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就是这个被敌人压着脑袋既不能躲也不能逃的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 拉芬蒂怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是..能量有点摄取过多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个..不是应该掺水喝的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的..我能上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起上次的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭你们俩的话一定能成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一第二隔板开启
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机师心跳数 血压 呼吸频率皆处于正常数值内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上部闸门 开启
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AID系统无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全系统All Green
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克斯·奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:35.01,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,660)}vox aura
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克斯·琳梵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.23,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,660)}vox rympha
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 小绿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧璐卡 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天都还没亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圆！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到复数欧比特从敌舰中出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:30.23,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(615,660)}ovid
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.69,0:12:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量是..！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克斯双机 即将和敌势接触
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:47.59,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(425,660)}vox
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快发射试作武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圆和小兰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了帮你报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来对于敌人的你不该予以同情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是听了前因后果之后真想给他一拳..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连本人都这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个过分的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫维拉裘里奥的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连拼上性命潜入敌营..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功夺取宝物的部下都..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因不合己意为由无情地抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况..是在知道你那淳朴心意的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是谁都可以得到忆痕的说..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好东西怎么不早拿出来用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没完没了啊 真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上援军就会到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺伊德？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人进入了伊古尼斯的驾驶舱！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.94,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(635,660)}ignis
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放大到显示屏上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上让她下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 已经上了发射序列
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不阻止我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的..真的..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来真的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆奇娜美？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不死心的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:15:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊古尼斯..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:15:58.96,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(635,660)}ignis
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃克斯系统启动..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不在AID系统的控制之下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百年难遇的天才吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也不错..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作主张的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会儿让你骂个够
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不晓得你在高心个什么劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要和哥哥这样说拜拜的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如干脆把哥哥给..！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 难不成想一个人..？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姆奇娜美！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上出击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我在这里继续待机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想一个人打三个人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多棒的夜晚~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..马上就要到早晨了么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的敌势有人机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后识别为敌势四号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昨晚出现在鸭川的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该道别了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥..哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裘裘！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 小圆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:19:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这全是没顾及到哥哥的心情 我自作主张的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错的全是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个..蠢姑娘！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被说成那样你还要包庇那个男人吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙..自己去死一死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那随便说什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一点都不了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一点都不明白我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有拜托你们帮我报仇啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,净说些“为了他人”之类的漂亮话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动服部还有这所有的一切..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所做的一切全都是为了自己啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这么想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:20:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到今天为止都一直是..这么..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这是..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圆！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是维拉裘里奥的目的..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能..为了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说..果然是..垃圾？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮回开启了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 运动服没了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书包里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那洗衣机里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.12,0:23:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 不会被偷走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.57,0:23:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 姆奇娜美？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难不成..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.44,0:23:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我偷的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.40,0:23:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.01,0:23:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛 小兰..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说我没有偷啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.70,0:23:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微试穿了一下而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.64,0:23:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是胸部附近实在有点紧..
